   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Click the object link under the Name column in the Map Objects table. </p>
            <stepresult>The Map Object page is displayed.</stepresult>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Scroll to the list of object fields. Click <uicontrol>New Map Field</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter information into the required fields to map the field between objects. Refer to the previous task for steps. </p>
            <p>
               <note type="note">
                  <p>When you map fields from the object page, the ObjectId is automatically populated.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol> or <uicontrol>Save &amp; Close</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
